description:
Eddie Donmez gives an overview of everything you need to know about Financial Markets in the year 2020 so far. 

In this session Eddie covers the following:

- Global Central Banks (0:21) 
- Global GDP (01:10)
- FAANG (01:59)
- Gold (03:50)
- Tesla (05:00)
- Oil (05:42)
- Yields At Record Lows, Inflation Is Coming (US Election) (06:31)
- What Is Coming Next? (08:06)
